Material: Rose Gold

Comes with Original Box And Original Papers





Patek Philippe gives the Reference 6002 Sky Moon Tourbillon a new look by combining the warm glow of rose gold with a Grand Feu brown enamel decoration. The double-faced case, crowns, slide piece, hour/minute hands and fold-over clasp are entirely hand-engraved with volutes and arabesques. The front dial combines Grand Feu champlevé and cloisonné enameling. This exceptional timepiece, the second most complicated Patek Philippe wristwatch (12 complications). Mechanical manually wound movement. Caliber R TO 27 QR SID LU CL. Sky Moon Tourbillon. Double-faced wristwatch. Minute repeater with “cathedral” gongs. Tourbillon. Front side: Perpetual calendar with retrograde date hand. Day, month, leap year in apertures. Hours and minutes of mean solar time. Moon phases. Reverse side: sidereal time, sky chart, phases and orbit of the moon. Grand Feu champlevé and cloisonné brown enamel, gold applied Roman numerals. 18K gold dial plate. Rose gold. Sapphire-crystal case back. Humidity- and dust-protected only (not water-resistant). Case diameter: 44 mm. Height: 17.35 mm. Alligator leather with square scales, hand-stitched, chestnut patinated. Hand-engraved fold-over clasp.

For sale is an Omega Deville with a Factory White Tapestry Saudi Arabia Stamp Dial.








This watch features a rare Saudi Arabia Stamp on the dial. The original owner of the watch had given a speech in Saudi Arabia around 25 years ago and was gifted this watch as a sign of appreciation by Saudi officials.








Included with the watch:





- Original Box: No





- Original Papers:No

- Model: DeVille





- Year: circa 1990’s





- Case material: Stainless Steel





- Case diameter: 32mm





- Bracelet: Omega Leather Strap





- Bracelet material: Leather





- Dial: Saudi Stamped Tapestry Dial





- Crystal: Sapphire








Features:





- Rare Saudi Arabia Stamped Dial








Movement:





- Omega Quartz Movement








Guarantee:





All of our watches undergo thorough inspection to ensure authenticity before we accept them in to our stock and offer them to the public. You can shop with full confidence knowing that everything we sell is genuine.








Warranty:





We provide 12 months warranty on all of our watches as standard. This excludes water damage, accidental damage or any damage caused by misuse.








Shipping:





We provide free next day insured & tracked shipping for all UK customers.








International shipping is also available - charges will vary based on country.

OMEGA first introduced the Seamaster 300 in 1957 - designed especially for divers and professionals who worked underwater. More than 60 years later, the timepiece has been completely upgraded with an enhanced form that is ready for a new generation of adventurers.





This 41 mm stainless steel model includes a black dial and a black oxalic anodized aluminium bezel with its diving scale filled with vintage Super-LumiNova. The recessed hour markers and open numerals feature Super-LumiNova, which is also present on the rhodium-plated hands.





Presented on an ergonomic stainless steel bracelet, this timepiece includes a transparent sapphire crystal caseback, enabling a clear view of the OMEGA Co-Axial Master Chronometer Calibre 8912.
